data.description: Opportunity awaits.  This majestic home just needs TLC to bring it back to life.  It offers 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  One bedroom/bath is downstairs along with Living room, dining room and kitchen.  Electrical has partial updates and plumbing was updated in the early 2000's. Painted a year and a half ago.  Large lot across the street from the river. The property zoning is being changed so that 4 cluster homes could be added.  Buyer to do due diligence.  House is in the Historical Society.
